# Shapes + shading: circle/ellipse fills plus dither_fill to fake a
# gradient (pixel art has no true per-pixel gradient fill).
clear
circle 8 8 7 #2a6f2a fill
dither_fill 2 2 8 8 #7fd67f #2a6f2a checkerboard
dither_fill 8 2 6 6 #cfffcf #7fd67f horizontal
ellipse 6 6 2 1 #eaffea fill
circle 8 8 7 #143d14
